name: King Skull - Cool Baby Vest (men)
description:
King Skull's first original design. 

The baby on the front is called George. Despite all his hair and his cool glasses, he was only a month old when this picture was taken. He hopes you like his vest.

The print is on a white Fruit of the Loom vest so you can be sure of quality.

We also supply the same vest but cut for women.

name: King Skull - Cool Baby Vest (women)
description:
King Skull's first original design. 

The baby on the front is called George. Despite all his hair and his cool glasses, he was only a month old when this picture was taken. He hopes you like his vest.

The print is on a white Fruit of the Loom 'lady fit' vest so you can be sure of quality. 

We also supply the same vest but cut for men.

name: SURE T-Shirt - Natural Inspiration (chocolate purple)
description: The "Natural Inspiration" t-shirt from Sure. The back of the tee carries a smaller version of the image on the front

name: Smoking Lady vest (yellow)
description: The "Smoking Lady" vest! The text surrounding her is about the colosseum. Why? We don't know, but it looks good. They are only available in one size but their loose style and design mean they are suitable for anyone up to a size 14.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Bob Marley (grey)
description: This t-shirt design from Sure's "Stitched Up" range shows off Bob Marley's dreadlocks perfectly. His hairbands are stitched on the print of the t-shirt and the Sure logo crosses the shoulder blades across the back.

name: Skull ripped vest
description: What else would King Skull supply but a women's vest with a skull on the front!!! This vest is suitable up to a size 12 but  will also look good on a smaller woman as it's designed to be a loose fit.

name: Cartoon Skull vest
description: We are King Skull and we bring you vests that have skulls on. Simple. These vests are small so one for the petite woman.

name: Camera vest (black)
description: These camera print t-shirts are only available in one size but their loose style and design mean they are suitable for anyone up to a size 14.

name: Headphones vest (pink)
description: The classic "headphones around the neck" design. They are only available in one size but their loose style and design mean they are suitable for anyone up to a size 14.

name: Sure vest - Elephant
description: Sure are a Thai brand so elephants play a huge part in lots of their designs. This cool women's vest is no different.

name: Sure vest - Cute elephant
description: You like your t-shirts cute??? Then this is for you.

name: Sure vest - Bob Marley
description: Sure seem to like Bob Marley...a lot. They make men's and kids t-shirts with him printed on, and now the women's vests are getting the treatment too.

name: Sure vest - Big Hand
description: Is it a hand? We're not sure...but in pink it's very cute for summer.

name: Sure vest - Big Face
description: This Sure vest is cut from one of the best men's t-shirts that Sure do. It's then shaped and tailored for a perfect women's fit.

name: Sure vest - 4Hands
description: We call it 4Hands but it should really be six because there are two more on the back. Made from cotton, Sure vests are high quality and ultra stylish with distressed edging around the neck and arms.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Bootsy Colins (terracotta)
description: Bootsy Colins is the man who put bass in your face!!! The funk bassist made his name with James Brown. Now he's on a Sure t-shirt stocked by King Skull. His hat is stitched in and there's extra stitching on the shoulder to give a 3D effect.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Jimi Hendrix (green)
description: Jimi Hendrix gets the Sure treatment. His headband is stitched into this t-shirt to make it stand out from the crowd.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Bob Marley (print)
description: If you love Bob Marley, then this is your t-shirt!!! We don't get many of these at King Skull so get it while you can.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Bob Marley (blue)
description: This t-shirt design from Sure's "Stitched Up" range shows off Bob Marley's dreadlocks perfectly. His hairbands are stitched on the print of the t-shirt and the Sure logo crosses the shoulder blades across the back.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Turn Over A New Life
description: The inscription at the bottom of this t-shirt reads "turn over a new life". We only stock it in dark green and it comes in Sure's trademark stretch material with creased effect. We stock it in medium but the nature of the material means it's suitable for anyone who wears and small, medium or large.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Magic Mushrooms
description: The Sure "Magic Mushroom" design t-shirt has that exact slogan on the front and the back of the tee.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Leopard
description: The Sure "Leopard" t-shirt carries a large leopard print on the front with a smaller one on the back.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Ghandi
description: This Sure t-shirt carries the image of Gandhi who led India to independence through non-violent protest. The tee also has one of Gandhi's quotes across the front and back. It reads "First they ignore you. Then they laugh at you. Then they fight you. Then you win". As with all Sure t-shirts, it is a medium but stretchy enough to be suitable for men who wear medium or large.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Elephant#2 (turquoise)
description: Another elephant t-shirt design from Sure. "Elephant Number Two" carries the Sure logo on the front left shoulder and across the back.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Elephant#2 (beige)
description: Another elephant t-shirt design from Sure. "Elephant Number Two" carries the Sure logo on the front left shoulder and across the back.

name: Pure Concepts - Bubbles
description: This is the perfect summer t-shirt. White with a full frontal print. The can at the bottom has "Pure Concepts" written on it with the bubbles reaching up to the shoulder.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Big Eye
description: Sure's "big eye" design only comes in blue. It has the Sure name across the shoulders on the back of the t-shirt. It's made from a stretchy, creased material so no need to iron!!! It comes in a medium but is suitable for those who wear medium to large.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Tigers (blue)
description: The "Tigers" t-shirt carries the slogan "Original Sure Tattoo" on the front and back with a pair of tigers on each side too. It also has a long arc of Thai writing but I'm afraid your guess is as good as ours as to the translation. All Sure t-shirts come in a medium, but their stretchy material make them suitable for men who wear small, medium or large.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Tigers (turquoise)
description: The "Tigers" t-shirt carries the slogan "Original Sure Tattoo" on the front and back with a pair of tigers on each side too. It also has a long arc of Thai writing but I'm afraid your guess is as good as ours as to the translation. All Sure t-shirts come in a medium, but their stretchy material make them suitable for men who wear small, medium or large.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Cherubs
description: The Sure cherubs t-shirt. As with all our t-shirts, it comes in a medium, but the stretchy nature of the material used by Sure means it is suitable for men who wear medium to large.

name: Pure Concepts - Happy Buddah (Blue)
description: This guy is all smiles as he takes up the whole front of the tee. Get some joy in your life with this little fella.

name: Sure T-Shirt - Natural Inspiration (purple)
description: The "Natural Inspiration" t-shirt from Sure. The back of the tee carries a smaller version of the image on the front

name: SURE T-Shirt - Natural Inspiration (maroon)
description: The "Natural Inspiration" t-shirt from Sure. The back of the tee carries a smaller version of the image on the front

name: Pure Concepts - Eledragon
description: Is it an elephant? Is it a dragon? We don't know but it looks cool. Has "Made in Thailand" written in script towards the bottom of the tee.

name: Sure Kids - Happy Buddah
description: This little fella looks like he's had his Ready Brek with a yellow glow around him. It reads "Happy Buddah" on the front and "Happy Buddah Senior" on the back.

name: Sure Kids - Elephant (green)
description: A cute little t-shirt from Sure. It reads "Respect Senior" across the front and "Senior" across the back.

name: Sure Kids - Laughing Buddah
description: This little buddah is riding a dragon and eating a bowl of rice. What more do you need from a t-shirt.

name: Sure Kids - Elephant (pink)
description: A cute little t-shirt from Sure. It reads "Respect Senior" across the front and "Senior" across the back.
